Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,养鬼吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,主演：安德鲁·罗宾逊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,主演：克莱尔·希金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,主演：肖恩·查普曼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,导演：克里夫·巴克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,您看上什么 科顿先生？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What's your pleasure, Mr. Cotton?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,盒子\N{\fnarial\fs12}The box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去吧 归你了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Take it, it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是\N{\fnarial\fs12}It always was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是其中一把钥匙\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's gotta be one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我都快冻死了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm going to freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 好了 - 也许有人把锁换了\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Okay, okay. -Well, maybe somebody changed the lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谁呢？谁会把锁换掉？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Like who? Who's gonna change this lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我也不知道 我只是瞎猜的\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well, I don't know. It was just a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 成功了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Ah. Success.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧\N{\fnarial\fs12}Voila.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 这里就是\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well, this is it--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们家的老宅\N{\fnarial\fs12}the old homestead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,恶心 一股潮湿的味道\N{\fnarial\fs12}Yuck. It smells damp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 已经.... 空置很长一段时间了 不是吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well, it's... been empty for a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们很快可以让它热闹起来\N{\fnarial\fs12}But we'll soon warm it up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,让它有家的感觉\N{\fnarial\fs12}and get it feeling like a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你多久没来这了？\N{\fnarial\fs12}How long since you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 差不多10年了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, the better part of 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老太太去世后 我想把它卖掉\N{\fnarial\fs12}I wanted to sell it after the old lady died,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但我弟弟弗兰克不同意\N{\fnarial\fs12}but I couldn't get Frank to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他需要个落脚点之类的地方\N{\fnarial\fs12}I guess he needed a hideout or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你来瞧瞧这个？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Would you look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fnarial\fs12}And don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这种东西对我来说毫无意义\N{\fnarial\fs12}this stuff means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,统统扔掉\N{\fnarial\fs12}It all goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为一半属于你弟弟\N{\fnarial\fs12}I thought half of it was your brother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没见过他到手的不要的 除非...\N{\fnarial\fs12}I've never known him to kick cash out of bed. Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能在哪儿坐牢呢\N{\fnarial\fs12}he's probably behind bars someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们整理前 得让克里斯蒂看看这个地方\N{\fnarial\fs12}we have to let Kirsty see this place before we do a thing to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她会喜欢的\N{\fnarial\fs12}She'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的 想搬到这儿来吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}You really want to move in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我看这里可比布鲁克林好多了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I suppose it's better than Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 别说了 朱莉娅\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, don't start, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么别说了？ - 听着\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Don't start what? -Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在这里顺利定居的\N{\fnarial\fs12}We can make it work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我工作不错 你回到了自家地盘\N{\fnarial\fs12}Now I've got a terrific job, you're back on your own turf--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会过得很幸福的\N{\fnarial\fs12}we can be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好好好 - 那还有什么异议呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}-All right, all right. -So what's the argument?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有异议啊 - 噢 老天\N{\fnarial\fs12}-No argument. -Oh, Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fnarial\fs12}Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌\N{\fnarial\fs12}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拉里 拉里\N{\fnarial\fs12}Larry! Larry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在哪儿呢？ - 在这儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Where are you? -In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有人占了屋子？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Squatters?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是弗兰克\N{\fnarial\fs12}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他在这儿住吗？ - 嗯 他来过\N{\fnarial\fs12}-He's here? -Well, he's been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 厨房里还留着些恶心东西\N{\fnarial\fs12}I mean, there's stuff in the kitchen you wouldn't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显 又是他的逃亡名场面之一\N{\fnarial\fs12}He's obviously made one of his famous getaways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,会是谁的电话呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁？\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fnarial\fs12}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂!\N{\fnarial\fs12}Kirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我通过了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I got through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太不容易了 你在哪儿呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Barely. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了一间公寓\N{\fnarial\fs12}I found a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说什么？ - 我说 我找到了一间公寓\N{\fnarial\fs12}-You what? -I said, I found a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我以为你暂时 会跟我们住一起\N{\fnarial\fs12}Wait, I thought you were going to stay with us for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fnarial\fs12}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你会喜欢这座房子的\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well, you'd like this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你会喜欢我的公寓的\N{\fnarial\fs12}You'd like my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很想让你来 看看这房子 它太与众不同了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'd really like you to see this house. It's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也许在接下来的几天中 我会找份工作\N{\fnarial\fs12}Maybe in the next couple of days. I gotta find myself a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢 甜心？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What for, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 你样子做够了吧 没必要...\N{\fnarial\fs12}Look, you've already made the gesture, there's no need--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 不是做样子 是我必须这么做\N{\fnarial\fs12}Dad, this isn't a gesture. This is something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 信任我一下吧 好吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come on and trust me a little, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明天给我电话 - 好的 再见\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Call me tomorrow. -I will. I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 爸爸\N{\fnarial\fs12}Bye, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样？\N{\fnarial\fs12}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不搬进来呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,周日我们就搬进来\N{\fnarial\fs12}We'll move in on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 通过这个地方时 小心门装饰条\N{\fnarial\fs12}Listen, look out for the moulding on the way through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 好的\N{\fnarial\fs12}- All right. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 后面没事吧？ - 是 是\N{\fnarial\fs12}- Are you all right back there? -Yeah yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可以 好了 直接把它搬到楼上去\N{\fnarial\fs12}All right, okay. Now just take it straight up the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 可以通过\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't worry, it'll get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 什么情况？ - 夹着我的手臂了！\N{\fnarial\fs12}-All right. What's the matter? -Hey, you got my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 好的 - 哦 老天\N{\fnarial\fs12}- All right, all right. -Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当心 - 哦\N{\fnarial\fs12}- Watch it. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们休息一下吧 伙计们\N{\fnarial\fs12}Let's take five, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你那儿收拾得怎么样了？\N{\fnarial\fs12}How's things in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,像扔了炸弹一样乱七八糟\N{\fnarial\fs12}Looks like a bomb dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有啤酒吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}You got any beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,冰箱里有一些\N{\fnarial\fs12}There's some in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那么...\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么不去拿呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}why don't I get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我现在无计可施\N{\fnarial\fs12}I've got nothing better to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,借过\N{\fnarial\fs12}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真是幸运的一天 - 嘿\N{\fnarial\fs12}-My lucky day. -Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想买张床吗？ - 不是很想\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Do you wanna buy a bed? -Not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克里斯蒂！ - 嘿\N{\fnarial\fs12}- Kirsty! -Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哈罗 甜心 到这儿来\N{\fnarial\fs12}Hello, sweetie. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给你们 - 哦 太好了\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Here you go. -Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这房子真大\N{\fnarial\fs12}This is a big house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你喜欢吗？ - 是的\N{\fnarial\fs12}-You like? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢\N{\fnarial\fs12}Me like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们能把这该死的床搬走 我就带你参观一番\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'll give you the grand tour if we ever get this goddamn bed moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 朱莉娅在这儿吗？ - 她在楼上\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Is Julia here? -She's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,注意 对她温和点儿 好吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Look, be gentle with her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她讨厌搬家 - 好意外哦\N{\fnarial\fs12}-She hates moving. -Surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克里斯蒂 - 好啦 我会友好点\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Kirsty. -Okay, all right. I'll be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们继续干体力活吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}You get on with the grunt work
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我给自己弄点咖啡 - 好主意\N{\fnarial\fs12}-and I'll make myself some coffee. -That's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 厨房在那儿 - 好的\N{\fnarial\fs12}-There's the kitchen. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fnarial\fs12}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是你女儿吗？- 啊哈\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Is that your daughter? -Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很像她妈妈 - 她妈妈已经过世了\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Got her mother's looks. -Her mother's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 该死\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以进来吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以进来吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是朱莉娅 对吗？ - 没错\N{\fnarial\fs12}-You're Julia, right? -That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哪位？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是弗兰克\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你丈夫的兄弟\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm brother Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 对\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我是来参加婚礼的\N{\fnarial\fs12}I--I came for the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那 我可以进来了吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well, can I come in or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 当然可以\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm sorry. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,热烈欢迎\N{\fnarial\fs12}You're very welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 听你这么说 我很欣慰\N{\fnarial\fs12}Yeah. Well, that's nice to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你有毛巾吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Do you have a towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你有毛巾吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Have you got a towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Kirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,浴室里有一条\N{\fnarial\fs12}There's one in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 顺便说一句 爸爸有没有告诉你 我找了一间公寓？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, by the way, did Daddy tell you I got a room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,房间不大 但挺好\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's not that big, but it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉娅\N{\fnarial\fs12}Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉娅\N{\fnarial\fs12}Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们祝什么呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What shall we drink to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,祝天赐良缘？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Wedded bliss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我很幸福\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm sure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你要让我吻新娘吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}You're gonna let me kiss the bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拉里怎么办呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What about Larry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了他\N{\fnarial\fs12}Forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉娅...朱莉娅...朱莉娅..\N{\fnarial\fs12}Julia... Julia... Julia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,需要把重量抬起 我的脚被压住了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I need to take the weight away from me, my foot's caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你明白吗？ - 明白了\N{\fnarial\fs12}-You got it? -I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我拉的时候 你往我这推\N{\fnarial\fs12}Now just push it to me as I pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,永远满足不了我\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's never enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉娅 朱...\N{\fnarial\fs12}Julia. Jul...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意为你做任何事\N{\fnarial\fs12}Ill do anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,任何事\N{\fnarial\fs12}Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口很深吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, is it deep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 我没有看\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't know. I haven't looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我怕血\N{\fnarial\fs12}You know me and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我快晕倒了 - 你不会晕倒\N{\fnarial\fs12}-I'm gonna faint. -You're not going to faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 他妈的\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我看看 - 他妈的\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Let me see. -Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 得去缝针\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, it's going to need stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要吐了 - 你不能吐\N{\fnarial\fs12}-I'm gonna throw up. -You're not going to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放松点儿 放松点儿 - 我要吐了\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Just take it easy, just take it easy. -I'm gonna throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事儿的\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's going to be all right
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们送你去医院\N{\fnarial\fs12}Let's get you to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是太笨了\N{\fnarial\fs12}So stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个小意外 他没事了\N{\fnarial\fs12}It was just an accident. He's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 你来开车好吗？ 得去缝针\N{\fnarial\fs12}Look, will you drive? He needs stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然可以 - 车钥匙在厨房里\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Yeah, sure. -The keys are in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我太笨了 - 没事的\N{\fnarial\fs12}-So stupid. - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 我真不是开玩笑\N{\fnarial\fs12}No no, I am not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那个医生一通乱戳....\N{\fnarial\fs12}This doctor is poking around
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.08,0:22:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,跟约瑟夫·门格勒一样毫无体贴和同情之心\N{\fs12}（约瑟夫·门格勒，人称“死亡天使”，德国纳粹党卫队军官和奥斯威辛集中营的医生）\N{\fnarial\fs12}with all the delicacy and compassion of Josef Mengele,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我警告他 听着 我要晕过去了\N{\fnarial\fs12}and I'm warning him, : Listen, I'm gonna pass out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他说 哦 你当然不会晕 老兄 你当然不会\N{\fnarial\fs12}He says, Oh no, of course you're not, old boy. Of course you're not
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.36,0:22:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道接着 我就躺在地板上了\N{\fnarial\fs12}The next thing you know, I'm on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他傻站在那儿 好像他才是需要帮助的人\N{\fnarial\fs12}and he's standing there like he's the one who needs help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能害怕你起诉他\N{\fnarial\fs12}He probably is afraid you're gonna sue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该起诉他！\N{\fnarial\fs12}I should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔 我应该起诉他 这些事你比较懂吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}Bill, I should do it. You know all about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我给你打电话 我们告他\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'll call you tomorrow. We'll sue his ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,医生啊\N{\fnarial\fs12}Doctors
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 亲爱的\N{\fnarial\fs12}That's right, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我可爱的女儿喝了什么呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}And what's my darling daughter drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.64,0:23:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不记得了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 朱莉娅 你想再来点起泡酒吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Listen, Julia, you want some more bubbly?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哦不 我不能再喝了 谢谢\N{\fnarial\fs12}Uh no. No more for me, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.72,0:23:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了 停\N{\fnarial\fs12}Okay. Okay, stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我都要站不稳了 - 那就躺下好了\N{\fnarial\fs12}-I'm not gonna be able to stand up. -So lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 我失陪了 我想去睡觉了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Would you all excuse me? I think I'm going to go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗？亲爱的？- 啊哈\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Are you all right, darling? -Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想 我们也都该走了 - 不行 比尔\N{\fnarial\fs12}-I think we ought to be making a move, too - No Bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行\N{\fnarial\fs12}Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是大喜之夜啊\N{\fnarial\fs12}This is the night of the paper hat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们庆祝得正欢呢 坐下吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}We're celebrating something, so sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fnarial\fs12}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:23:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,明天你们来我们家吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}You'll have to come to us next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.19,0:24:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对 很快就再见面了 我很高兴你们回来了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Yeah, real soon. I'm glad you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fnarial\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 晚安 - 晚安\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Good night. -Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还痛吗？ - 什么？\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Does it still hurt? -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.00,0:24:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 不 只有喝酒时才痛\N{\fnarial\fs12}No, only when I drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.12,0:25:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 老天\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.20,0:25:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh! Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.28,0:25:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,滚出去！\N{\fnarial\fs12}out！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.88,0:25:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉娅\N{\fnarial\fs12}Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.52,0:26:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我的老天\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.88,0:26:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看我\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.32,0:26:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谁？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Who--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.84,0:26:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\fnarial\fs12}who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.76,0:26:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我说不要看\N{\fnarial\fs12}I said don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.22,0:26:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我\N{\fnarial\fs12}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.88,0:26:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 你是谁\N{\fnarial\fs12}Tell me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.82,0:26:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是弗兰克\N{\fnarial\fs12}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.68,0:26:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnarial\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.64,0:26:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fnarial\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.12,0:26:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 我就是弗兰克\N{\fnarial\fs12}Believe me, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.44,0:26:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是我\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.50,0:26:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他滴在地板上的血 复活了我\N{\fnarial\fs12}His blood on the floor, it brought me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.20,0:26:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,复活？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Back?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.76,0:27:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,从哪儿？\N{\fnarial\fs12}From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.08,0:27:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我 行吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Just help me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.64,0:27:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 老天 帮帮我\N{\fnarial\fs12}Please, God, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.32,0:27:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有人 - 等等\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Somebody -Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.52,0:27:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能就这样抛下我 你不能\N{\fnarial\fs12}You can't leave me like this. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.88,0:27:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我做什么呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.12,0:28:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,血已经让我恢复到这个程度\N{\fnarial\fs12}The blood brought me this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.28,0:28:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要更多的血\N{\fnarial\fs12}I need more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.88,0:28:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你得帮我痊愈\N{\fnarial\fs12}You have to heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.08,0:28:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fnarial\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.38,0:28:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.96,0:28:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂？我以为你走了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Kirsty? I thought I'd lost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.16,0:28:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我在这儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}No, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.00,0:28:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fnarial\fs12}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.76,0:29:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不留在拉里家呢？ 有足够的空间\N{\fnarial\fs12}So why didn't you stay at Larry's house? There's plenty of room.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.64,0:29:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是啊 有空间 但有朱莉娅在\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, yeah, there's room, and there's Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.23,0:29:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我明白了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Ah. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.28,0:29:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她和你一样 那么客套\N{\fnarial\fs12}She's like you. She's so damn polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.72,0:29:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是吗？ 代表什么？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, yeah? Meaning what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.04,0:29:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我不知道 她紧张而且冷淡\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, I don't know. She's uptight and frigid.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.40,0:29:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,请再说一遍\N{\fnarial\fs12}I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.56,0:29:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吧 你就是这样 ~“请再说一遍”\N{\fnarial\fs12}See, there you go. ~ "I beg your pardon."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.60,0:29:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 不是所有人都冷淡吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}Hey, we're not all frigid.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.52,0:29:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 不么？ - 噢 不啊\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Oh, no? -Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.08,0:29:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 不么？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.22,0:29:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 不\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.36,0:29:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到的不是这样\N{\fnarial\fs12}That's not what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.84,0:29:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那你一定是没有遇到正确的人\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well, you must have been speaking to all the wrong people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.92,0:30:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,任何事都可以吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.88,0:30:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,任何事\N{\fnarial\fs12}Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.52,0:30:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你会照办吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}You'll do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.63,0:30:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我会\N{\fnarial\fs12}Yes... I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.36,0:32:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂?克里斯蒂?\N{\fnarial\fs12}Ki rsty? Ki rsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.12,0:32:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克里斯蒂! - 啊！\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Kirsty! -Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.12,0:32:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗？ - 对\N{\fnarial\fs12}-You all right? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.36,0:32:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.20,0:32:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我做了个梦\N{\fnarial\fs12}I--Iwas dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.08,0:32:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fnarial\fs12}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.29,0:32:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好 亲爱的\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm all right, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.15,0:32:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想确认一下你没事\N{\fnarial\fs12}I just wanted to make sure you were okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.71,0:32:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再好不过了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Never better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.40,0:32:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在你去好好睡觉吧 - 好\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Now you sleep well, okay? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.99,0:33:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 甜心\N{\fnarial\fs12}I love you, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.05,0:33:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你 爸爸\N{\fnarial\fs12}I love you too, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.16,0:33:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fnarial\fs12}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.32,0:33:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是谁呢？ - 她做了个噩梦\N{\fnarial\fs12}Who was it? -She had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.20,0:33:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁？ - 克里斯蒂\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Who? -Kirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.52,0:33:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂\N{\fnarial\fs12}Kirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.44,0:33:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没什么意思，对吗？ - 什么？\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Not much fun, is it? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.88,0:33:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人喝闷酒\N{\fnarial\fs12}Drinking alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.84,0:34:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么意思\N{\fnarial\fs12}Not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.00,0:34:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也许...\N{\fnarial\fs12}I thought maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.55,0:34:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,额\N{\fnarial\fs12}well...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.72,0:34:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们都是一个人 也许我们可以一起喝\N{\fnarial\fs12}if we're both on our own, maybe we could have a drink together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.09,0:34:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.16,0:34:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你得知道 我不是经常...\N{\fnarial\fs12}You know, it's not often that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.03,0:34:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\fnarial\fs12}you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.84,0:34:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,任何事都有第一次\N{\fnarial\fs12}There's a first time for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.88,0:34:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没错儿 对\N{\fnarial\fs12}That's right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.00,0:34:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这倒是真的\N{\fnarial\fs12}I suppose that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.73,0:34:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要....... 来杯酒呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Would you... like a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.40,0:34:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 不 不\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, no no no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.56,0:34:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经过量了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm well over my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.11,0:34:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 有趣的是\N{\fnarial\fs12}You know, it's funny,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.44,0:34:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...我..\N{\fnarial\fs12}but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.12,0:35:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉 我们已经认识好多年了 知道吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}I feel like I've known you for years, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.63,0:35:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.93,0:35:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你带我来这儿就是为了这个的 不是吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's what you brought me here for, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.95,0:35:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,额 不是吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.72,0:35:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是的 对\N{\fnarial\fs12}I suppose so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.88,0:35:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是怎么回事呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}So what's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.67,0:35:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}Let's get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.60,0:35:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的不会改变主意了吧？\N{\fnarial\fs12}You're not gonna change your fucking mind, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.16,0:35:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.16,0:35:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到楼上去吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}Let's go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.60,0:35:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好的 对不起 好吗 好的\N{\fnarial\fs12}Okay okay. Sorry, okay? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.04,0:35:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fnarial\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.69,0:36:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是卧室\N{\fnarial\fs12}This isn't the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.80,0:36:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fnarial\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.04,0:36:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那 怎么回事呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}So what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.60,0:36:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没必非要用床 对吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}We don't need a bed, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.40,0:36:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,额 没错 我想没必要\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well, no, I suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.00,0:36:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直更喜欢地板\N{\fnarial\fs12}I've always preferred the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.83,0:36:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 任何事都有第一次 嗯？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh. First time for everything, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.16,0:36:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不...\N{\fnarial\fs12}Why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.16,0:36:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,把外套脱掉呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}take your jacket off?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.24,0:36:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 为什么不呢\N{\fnarial\fs12}Yeah, why don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.48,0:37:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不一起脱？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Why don't you do the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.48,0:37:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我会的\N{\fnarial\fs12}Maybe I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.24,0:37:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你太漂亮了\N{\fnarial\fs12}You're very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.66,0:37:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.04,0:37:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你知道自己漂亮\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, you know you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.04,0:37:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我见过的 最可爱的女人\N{\fnarial\fs12}Loveliest woman... I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.15,0:37:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 老天爷\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.44,0:37:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.57,0:37:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,等一会儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}Just one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.72,0:37:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喝了太多的酒\N{\fnarial\fs12}Too much drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.32,0:37:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,得清空膀胱\N{\fnarial\fs12}Empty the old bladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.60,0:37:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你锁了门？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Did you lock this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.56,0:37:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了！求你了！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.24,0:38:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别看我\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.16,0:39:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷\N{\fnarial\fs12}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.00,0:39:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.71,0:39:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我复原了\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's making me whole again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.49,0:40:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,洒出的每一滴血 都能让我的骨头长出新肉\N{\fnarial\fs12}Every drop of blood you spill puts more flesh on my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.57,0:40:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都希望这样 不是吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}And we both want that, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.59,0:40:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fnarial\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.60,0:40:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.68,0:40:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的 过来 我想摸摸你\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come here, damn you, I wanna touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.04,0:40:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,到爸爸这儿来\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.72,0:40:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉娅！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Julia!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.07,0:41:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉娅\N{\fnarial\fs12}Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.44,0:41:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,出来 快出来 你在哪儿呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come out, come out, wherever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.77,0:41:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉娅 我在叫你 你听不到吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Julia, I was calling for you. Didn't you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.00,0:41:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你在里面吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.28,0:41:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你要吃曲奇吗 亲爱的\N{\fnarial\fs12}You want a cookie, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.00,0:41:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点不舒服\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm feeling sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.16,0:41:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 宝贝 要我拿点什么给你吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, babe. Is there anything I can get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.36,0:41:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,来杯白兰地吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}Maybe a--a brandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.26,0:41:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就来\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.44,0:41:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我下来...马上\N{\fnarial\fs12}Ill be down... in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.84,0:41:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fnarial\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.44,0:41:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不着急\N{\fnarial\fs12}There's no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.44,0:42:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.32,0:42:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 - 我很痛\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Oh. -I'm hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.46,0:42:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,痛？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.60,0:42:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的神经又长好了\N{\fnarial\fs12}My nerves are beginning to work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.36,0:42:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.80,0:42:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一个 也许两个...\N{\fnarial\fs12}One more, maybe two...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.88,0:42:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-  没有下次了 - 让我彻底恢复\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Not again. -to heal me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.64,0:42:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这样在他们开始追杀我之前 我们可以从这逃走\N{\fnarial\fs12}Then we can be away from here before they start to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.04,0:42:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁？ - 修道士\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Who? -The Cenobites.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.24,0:42:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们发现我逃脱只是时间问题\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's only a matter of time before they find I've slipped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.26,0:42:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须离开这儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}I must get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.94,0:42:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉娅？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.00,0:42:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.62,0:43:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等我一小会儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.40,0:43:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,放些音乐 好吗 宝贝？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Put on some music. Will you, babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.08,0:43:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fnarial\fs12}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.05,0:43:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的拉里 还是那么听话\N{\fnarial\fs12}Poor Larry, obedient as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.76,0:43:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你小声点儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.18,0:43:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不想让你的宝贝听见\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't want babe to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.11,0:43:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你弄痛我了\N{\fnarial\fs12}You're hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.80,0:43:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会欺骗我 对吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}You won't cheat me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.84,0:43:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你会留下来 帮我\N{\fnarial\fs12}You'll stay with me, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.24,0:43:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 我们能像以前一样 永远在一起\N{\fnarial\fs12}Then we can be together the way we were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.32,0:43:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在属于彼此\N{\fnarial\fs12}We belong to each other now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.85,0:43:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,同甘 共苦\N{\fnarial\fs12}For better, for worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.75,0:43:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有真爱\N{\fnarial\fs12}Like love...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.29,0:43:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,至死不渝\N{\fnarial\fs12}only real.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.28,0:44:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我是新来的 您得等等才行\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm sorry--I'm new here. You're gonna have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.40,0:44:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你别乱动 好吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Could you not do that, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.16,0:44:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,经理在哪儿呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Where's the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.08,0:44:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是个问题 因为他现在出去吃午餐了\N{\fnarial\fs12}That's a problem too, because he's out to lunch right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.32,0:44:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见负责的人\N{\fnarial\fs12}I want to see somebody in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.28,0:44:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那您得等等了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Then you're gonna have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.76,0:44:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不好意思 - 我才不好意思！\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Excuse me. -Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.84,0:44:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.64,0:44:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,快点放回去\N{\fnarial\fs12}Give those back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.11,0:44:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我的天啊\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh myGod.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.36,0:44:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\fnarial\fs12}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.80,0:44:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我滚出去\N{\fnarial\fs12}You get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.46,0:45:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 嗨\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Hi. -Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.28,0:45:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只是过来想看看 你下班之后有什么安排\N{\fnarial\fs12}Just came by to see what you're doing after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.76,0:45:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.00,0:45:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怪事 - 什么？\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Something weird. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.72,0:45:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\fnarial\fs12}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.60,0:45:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定我们不会被打搅吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}You're sure we're not gonna be interrupted?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.24,0:45:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很确定\N{\fnarial\fs12}Quite sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.56,0:45:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是...额\N{\fnarial\fs12}Only I--uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.32,0:45:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢小心点\N{\fnarial\fs12}I like to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.32,0:46:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以尝到味道了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I can taste that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.20,0:46:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我很久没尝到任何味道了\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's a long time since I tasted anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.56,0:47:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你答应过 会给我一个解释\N{\fnarial\fs12}You promised me an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.92,0:47:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是它\N{\fnarial\fs12}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.12,0:47:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我看看 - 不 不要碰它！\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Let me see. -No, don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.08,0:47:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,它很危险 它会打开门\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's dangerous. It opens doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.52,0:47:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的门？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What kind of doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.56,0:47:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这门可通往快乐的天堂 或是痛苦的地狱\N{\fnarial\fs12}Doors to the pleasures of heaven or hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.28,0:47:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎是哪个\N{\fnarial\fs12}I didn't care which.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.68,0:47:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我原以为我已经经历了人生的极限\N{\fnarial\fs12}I thought I'd gone to the limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.72,0:47:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我没有 修道士给了我超越极限的体验\N{\fnarial\fs12}I hadn't. The Cenobites gave me an experience beyond limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.76,0:47:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦与快乐 纠缠交错\N{\fnarial\fs12}Pain and pleasure... indivisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.34,0:48:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不能再把我带回去\N{\fnarial\fs12}They won't get me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.28,0:48:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我得活下去 而你得帮我 好吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm going to live and you're going to help me, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.89,0:48:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fnarial\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.28,0:48:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们永远不会找到我们\N{\fnarial\fs12}They'll never find us,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.27,0:48:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在这茫茫的人世间\N{\fnarial\fs12}not in the whole wide world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.00,0:48:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嘭嘭击中他了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Boom Boom has got him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.48,0:48:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嘭嘭击中他了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Boom Boom has got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.40,0:48:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他又被击倒了\N{\fnarial\fs12}He's knocked down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.16,0:48:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你讨厌看这种东西\N{\fnarial\fs12}I thought this kind of stuff made you sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.92,0:48:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过更可怕的\N{\fnarial\fs12}I've seen worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.55,0:48:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.16,0:48:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊\N{\fnarial\fs12}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.64,0:48:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也可以看点别的\N{\fnarial\fs12}Cause we can watch something else
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.04,0:48:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快点！干掉他！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come on! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.08,0:49:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！不！不！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Ah! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.78,0:49:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么声音？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.16,0:49:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我没有把楼上的窗户关好 我去看看\N{\fnarial\fs12}I think I left a window open upstairs. I'll go see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.09,0:49:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不用\N{\fnarial\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.14,0:49:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拉里 那里没什么\N{\fnarial\fs12}Larry! It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.04,0:49:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,拉里！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Larry!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.95,0:49:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底怎么啦？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What's the matter with you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.27,0:49:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只是...是因为我害怕打雷声\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's just that I hate the thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.98,0:49:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.55,0:49:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你很安全\N{\fnarial\fs12}You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.99,0:49:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你在发抖\N{\fnarial\fs12}You're trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.68,0:49:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么好怕的\N{\fnarial\fs12}There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.36,0:49:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\fnarial\fs12}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.09,0:49:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的应该去看看\N{\fnarial\fs12}I really should check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.06,0:50:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别上去 求你了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't go up there, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.44,0:50:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起上去 来吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}We'll both go up. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.84,0:50:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拉里 求你了 - 别担心 来吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Larry, please! -Don't worry about it. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.52,0:50:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别进去 - 没事的 没事的\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Don't. -It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.20,0:50:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是老鼠\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's probably a rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.16,0:50:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你\N{\fnarial\fs12}I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.60,0:50:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么好怕的\N{\fnarial\fs12}There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.68,0:50:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下楼去吧 我会让一切好起来\N{\fnarial\fs12}Let's go downstairs. I'll make it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.04,0:51:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 光线够了\N{\fnarial\fs12}No, this is enough light.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.32,0:51:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 来吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}Let's go, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.31,0:51:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们进去\N{\fnarial\fs12}Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.11,0:51:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不错\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.60,0:51:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不错 不错\N{\fnarial\fs12}Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.88,0:52:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnarial\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.36,0:52:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fnarial\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.96,0:52:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不 求求你不要 不 求你了！\N{\fnarial\fs12}No, please don't. No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.52,0:52:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了了 求你了！\N{\fnarial\fs12}I can't bear it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.09,0:52:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,求你别这样！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.04,0:52:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.68,0:52:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,求你停下来！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.00,0:52:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了了！求你别这样！\N{\fnarial\fs12}I can't bear it! Please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.04,0:52:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.14,0:52:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 一分钟之前\N{\fnarial\fs12}I mean, one minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.20,0:52:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你扑上来缠我 但接着就...\N{\fnarial\fs12}you're all over me, and the next...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.30,0:53:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你真让我弄不懂\N{\fnarial\fs12}I just don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.84,0:53:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.08,0:53:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们不该回到这儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}Maybe we shouldn't have come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.68,0:53:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,住在布鲁克林绝对不会更糟\N{\fnarial\fs12}Brooklyn certainly wasn't any worse than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.00,0:53:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fnarial\fs12}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.04,0:53:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你很爱她 那肯定是她有 值得你爱的地方\N{\fnarial\fs12}You love her, so there must be something worth loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.20,0:53:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望真的那么简单就好了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I wish it were that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.22,0:53:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在有大麻烦了 孩子\N{\fnarial\fs12}I've got a real problem here, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.82,0:53:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她甚至不愿意离开房子\N{\fnarial\fs12}She doesn't even want to leave the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.80,0:53:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.12,0:53:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像她在...\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's like she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.04,0:53:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,等待着什么似的\N{\fnarial\fs12}waiting for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.84,0:53:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.24,0:53:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.68,0:53:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.56,0:53:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,难倒我了\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's way beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.24,0:53:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fnarial\fs12}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.20,0:54:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你能.. 你能...\N{\fnarial\fs12}Could you-- would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.12,0:54:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有空去坐坐吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}stop by sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.20,0:54:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,试试跟她交朋友？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Try to make friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.64,0:54:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fnarial\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.20,0:54:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢？ 也许她只是想找个说话的人\N{\fnarial\fs12}Who knows,maybe all she needs is somebody to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.84,0:54:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不能爱他 - 你知道 我不爱他\N{\fnarial\fs12}-You can't love him. -You know I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.16,0:54:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那 有什么坏处呢？ - 我说了不行\N{\fnarial\fs12}-So where's the harm? -I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.56,0:54:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 在修道士找来之前 再去给我找个人\N{\fnarial\fs12}Then find me somebody else, before they come looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.91,0:54:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,马上！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.24,0:55:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我...额\N{\fnarial\fs12}I... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.28,0:55:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我很孤单\N{\fnarial\fs12}I get lonely sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.53,0:55:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都是如此\N{\fnarial\fs12}Everybody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.69,0:55:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.64,0:55:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是做什么？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What is this,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.57,0:55:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,做游戏吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.84,0:55:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fnarial\fs12}Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.36,0:56:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天啊 救命\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, Christ! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.24,0:56:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,别动！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.45,0:56:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快出去！ - 求你了\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Get out of here! -Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.16,0:56:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他杀我\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't let him kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.52,0:57:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊\N{\fnarial\fs12}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.48,0:58:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnarial\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.44,0:58:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克里斯蒂 我是弗兰克 弗兰克叔叔 - 不\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Kirsty, it's Frank. It's Uncle Frank. -No!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.04,0:58:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还记得我 - 不\N{\fnarial\fs12}-You remember. -No!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.84,0:58:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到爸爸这儿来 - 他妈的放开我！\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Come to Daddy. -Get the fuck off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.25,0:58:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你长大了 你很漂亮\N{\fnarial\fs12}You've grown. You're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.87,0:58:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别...别碰我！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't-- don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.20,0:58:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我 否则我发誓...\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't touch me or so help me
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.35,0:58:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做什么呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.18,0:58:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做什么呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.02,0:58:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么可害怕的\N{\fnarial\fs12}There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.04,0:58:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢说 你让你爸爸很自豪吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}I bet you make your daddy so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.96,0:58:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是 小美人？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't you, beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.60,0:58:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是真的\N{\fnarial\fs12}This isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.67,0:58:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我常常这么告诉自己\N{\fnarial\fs12}I used to tell myself that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.08,0:58:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾试图假装 所有的痛苦 都只是一场梦\N{\fnarial\fs12}Used to try and pretend I was dreaming all the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.48,0:58:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不要自欺欺人了\N{\fnarial\fs12}But don't you kid yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.36,0:58:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有些事必须忍受\N{\fnarial\fs12}Some things have to be endured,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.92,0:58:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才能让快乐更甜美\N{\fnarial\fs12}and that's what makes the pleasures so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.64,0:59:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！\N{\fnarial\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.80,0:59:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.48,0:59:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 - 把它还给我！\N{\fnarial\fs12}-No. -Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.06,0:59:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}You want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.87,0:59:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次机会\N{\fnarial\fs12}One last time:
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.19,0:59:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把盒子还给我\N{\fnarial\fs12}give me that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.08,0:59:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想要吗？ - 把盒子还给我！\N{\fnarial\fs12}-You want it? -Give me the box!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.28,0:59:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要吗？他妈去拿啊！\N{\fnarial\fs12}You want it? Fucking have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.92,0:59:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fnarial\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.63,0:59:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂\N{\fnarial\fs12}Kirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.21,0:59:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,到爸爸这儿来\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.88,1:00:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我是弗兰克 你记得吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's Frank. You remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.08,1:00:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是弗兰克叔叔\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's  Uncle Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.24,1:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.88,1:01:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了\N{\fnarial\fs12}You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.92,1:01:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好孩子 - 出什么事了？\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Good girl. -What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.72,1:01:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我去叫医生 - 等等 我怎么到这儿的？\N{\fnarial\fs12}-I'll get the doctor. -Wait a minute. How did I get here?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.60,1:01:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上就回\N{\fnarial\fs12}I won't be a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.44,1:01:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 回床上去\N{\fnarial\fs12}Please, get back into bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.08,1:01:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我得给我爸爸打电话\N{\fnarial\fs12}I have to call my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.68,1:01:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这个很容易安排 但首先 回床上去\N{\fnarial\fs12}That's easily arranged, but first, back into bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.12,1:01:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这很重要 真的很重要\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's important. It really is--
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.80,1:01:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的事情先来\N{\fnarial\fs12}First things first.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.26,1:01:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和你谈过之后 会让你打电话的\N{\fnarial\fs12}We'll get you a telephone after we've talked.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.20,1:01:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？想起什么了吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What about this? Ring any bells?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.20,1:01:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你紧紧地抓着它不放\N{\fnarial\fs12}You were hanging onto it like grim death.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.25,1:01:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不记得了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.84,1:01:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 警察想跟你问话 你知道吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well, the police will want to speak to you. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.66,1:01:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.04,1:01:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 也许这个能让你记起来吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}In the meantime, maybe this will jog your memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.72,1:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕\N{\fnarial\fs12}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.92,1:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快打开！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Open!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.72,1:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 快点啊！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.83,1:06:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你打开了盒子\N{\fnarial\fs12}The box. You opened it,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.04,1:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就来了\N{\fnarial\fs12}we came.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.05,1:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个拼图盒子罢了！\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's just a puzzle box!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.18,1:07:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不是\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.60,1:07:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是召唤我们的方式\N{\fnarial\fs12}It is a means to summon us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.84,1:07:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是谁？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.68,1:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,极致体验的探索者\N{\fnarial\fs12}Explorers in the further regions of experience:
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.43,1:07:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,彼之魔鬼 汝之天使\N{\fnarial\fs12}demons to some, angels to others.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.49,1:07:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是个误会\N{\fnarial\fs12}It was a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.80,1:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不...我并不想把它打开的\N{\fnarial\fs12}I didn't--I didn't mean to open it!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.52,1:07:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是个误会\N{\fnarial\fs12}It was a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.72,1:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以...回到地狱\N{\fnarial\fs12}You can all... go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.54,1:07:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 如无所获 不得离开\N{\fnarial\fs12}We can't. Not alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.15,1:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你破解了盒子\N{\fnarial\fs12}You solved the box,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.12,1:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才来的 现在你得随我们走\N{\fnarial\fs12}we came. Now you must come with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.60,1:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,品味我们的快乐\N{\fnarial\fs12}Taste our pleasures
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.24,1:07:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,求你们了 走开 放了我吧！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Please, go away and leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.75,1:07:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 请别流泪\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, no tears, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.52,1:07:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是对美好磨难的一种浪费\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's a waste of good suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.20,1:07:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等等！等等！等等！ 拜托你们等等！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Wait! Wait! Wait! Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.51,1:07:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间争论了\N{\fnarial\fs12}No time for argument.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.60,1:07:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们以前也这么做过 对吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}You've done this before, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.24,1:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很多 很多次了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Many, many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.32,1:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有对一个叫弗兰克.科顿的男人做过吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}To a man called Frank Cotton?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.93,1:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是的\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.16,1:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他从你们手里跑掉了\N{\fnarial\fs12}He escaped you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.32,1:08:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 无人能从我们手里逃走 - 他成功了 我见到他了\N{\fnarial\fs12}- Nobody escapes us. - He did. I've seen him.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.24,1:08:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不可能！ - 他还活着！\N{\fnarial\fs12}- Impossible. -He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.20,1:08:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,即使他从我们手中逃脱\N{\fnarial\fs12}Supposing he had escaped us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.68,1:08:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那又与你何干？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What has that to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.93,1:08:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我可以... 我可以带你们去找他\N{\fnarial\fs12}I--I can-- I can lead you to him,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.16,1:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以带他回去 代替我\N{\fnarial\fs12}and you can take him back instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.36,1:08:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们更钟意你\N{\fnarial\fs12}Perhaps we'd prefer you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.12,1:08:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听到他亲口认罪\N{\fnarial\fs12}I want to hear him confess himself,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.20,1:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后也许...\N{\fnarial\fs12}then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.28,1:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也许\N{\fnarial\fs12}maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.28,1:08:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如若你敢欺瞒我们...\N{\fnarial\fs12}But if you cheat us...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.28,1:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会把你的灵魂撕碎\N{\fnarial\fs12}We'll tear your soul apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.96,1:08:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她会把一切告诉他们\N{\fnarial\fs12}She'll tell them everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.16,1:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不会 她会先去警告拉里\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't think so. She'll want to warn Larry first.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.64,1:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可能现在就是她打的电话...\N{\fnarial\fs12}That's probably her now...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.08,1:08:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 或是警察 - 那没有任何区别\N{\fnarial\fs12}-or the police. -It doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.96,1:08:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你不在乎吗？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Don't you care?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.64,1:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我在乎的是新皮肤\N{\fnarial\fs12}What I care about is a new skin.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.36,1:09:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们得离开\N{\fnarial\fs12}Maybe we should just leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.24,1:09:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样离开吗？看看我\N{\fnarial\fs12}Like this? Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.64,1:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能就待在这儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}We can't just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.12,1:09:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥哥很快就会回家\N{\fnarial\fs12}My brother will be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.26,1:09:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.56,1:09:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知从何说起\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't know where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.53,1:09:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.76,1:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好自己看看吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's best you see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.38,1:09:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我走时 她还安然无恙\N{\fnarial\fs12}I left her here safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.24,1:09:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至把门都锁上了\N{\fnarial\fs12}I even locked the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.36,1:09:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但她现在不在这儿了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well, she's not here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.24,1:09:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找她\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'll start looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.60,1:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也许她回...\N{\fnarial\fs12}Maybe she's gone back to...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.00,1:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,回她爸爸的房子去了\N{\fnarial\fs12}to her father's house.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.76,1:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.48,1:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 是我！克里斯蒂！让我进去！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Daddy, it's me, it's Kirsty! Let me in!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.49,1:10:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 让我进去！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Daddy, let me in!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.49,1:11:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克里斯蒂 很晚了 - 我爸爸在哪儿？\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Kirsty? It's very late. -Where is my dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.39,1:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 出什么事了？ - 我想见我爸爸\N{\fnarial\fs12}-What's the matter? -I want to see my father!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.16,1:11:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fnarial\fs12}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.53,1:11:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪儿？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.08,1:11:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪儿？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.80,1:11:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.04,1:11:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.69,1:11:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爸爸 你没事 你没事 - 当然 我很好 我很好\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Daddy, you're okay. You're all right. -Sure I am. I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.28,1:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事！- 没事的\N{\fnarial\fs12}-You're okay! -It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.18,1:11:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我真怕你出事\N{\fnarial\fs12}I was so afraid that something happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.70,1:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道\N{\fnarial\fs12}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.76,1:11:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我得跟你谈谈\N{\fnarial\fs12}I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.00,1:11:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fnarial\fs12}Yeah. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.52,1:11:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了 宝贝 朱丽娅把一切都告诉我了\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's okay, baby. Julia told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.52,1:11:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不是的 你得明白...\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, no, see...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.29,1:11:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你弟弟弗兰克在楼上\N{\fnarial\fs12}your brother Frank is upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.32,1:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他在楼上 他想要你的命\N{\fnarial\fs12}He's upstairs and he's trying to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.24,1:12:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他会杀了你！ - 不会 等等 等等 等等\N{\fnarial\fs12}-He's gonna kill you! -No, wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.68,1:12:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克做的事儿难以名状\N{\fnarial\fs12}Whatever Frank did was unspeakable.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.50,1:12:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,难以名状\N{\fnarial\fs12}Unspeakable.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.96,1:12:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但你得相信我\N{\fnarial\fs12}But believe me,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.80,1:12:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一切都结束了\N{\fnarial\fs12}it's finished with now.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.04,1:12:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么结束了？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Why is it finished?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.66,1:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他走了\N{\fnarial\fs12}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.88,1:12:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,“走了”是什么意思？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What does 'gone' mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.79,1:12:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了 克里斯蒂\N{\fnarial\fs12}He's dead, Kirsty.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.76,1:12:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个疯子 宝贝\N{\fnarial\fs12}He was insane, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.76,1:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他是条疯狗 我不得不帮他摆脱痛苦\N{\fnarial\fs12}A mad dog. I had to put him out of his misery.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.17,1:12:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷 场面好惨\N{\fnarial\fs12}Jesus, what a scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.64,1:12:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等我感觉好点以后\N{\fnarial\fs12}And when I'm feeling better,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.85,1:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去找警察 向他们说明白\N{\fnarial\fs12}I'll go to the police and try to make them understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.02,1:12:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,天知道...\N{\fnarial\fs12}God knows...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.96,1:12:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我都搞不懂自己\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't really understand myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.26,1:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他有没有伤害你 宝贝？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Did he hurt you, baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.56,1:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我很好\N{\fnarial\fs12}No, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.92,1:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了更好 可怜的弗兰克\N{\fnarial\fs12}He's better off dead. Poor Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.29,1:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信\N{\fnarial\fs12}I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.20,1:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不敢相信 - 相信这一切吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}-I don't believe this. -Believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.41,1:13:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我得看看他\N{\fnarial\fs12}I need to see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.08,1:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行 没必要了 - 不 我要看\N{\fnarial\fs12}-No, you don't. -Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.64,1:13:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,必须！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.95,1:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,带她去看看\N{\fnarial\fs12}Show her.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.80,1:14:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要这个凶手\N{\fnarial\fs12}We want the man who did this.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.72,1:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnarial\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.72,1:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这不是咱们说好的\N{\fnarial\fs12}No, that wasn't the deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.48,1:14:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我父亲 你们不能抓他\N{\fnarial\fs12}He's my father and you can't have him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.96,1:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！\N{\fnarial\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.24,1:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！让开！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Ah! Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.30,1:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂...\N{\fnarial\fs12}Kirsty...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.66,1:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,让开！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.52,1:15:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.00,1:15:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间了\N{\fnarial\fs12}There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.48,1:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 不 等等 我跟你说过 现在一切都结束了\N{\fnarial\fs12}Wait, no wait. I told you all that's over with now.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.88,1:15:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不 还没有 我们得离开这儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}No, it's not! We've got to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.76,1:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不 留在我们身边\N{\fnarial\fs12}No, stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.72,1:15:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这会过得很开心\N{\fnarial\fs12}We can all be happy here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.57,1:15:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnarial\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.86,1:15:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,到爸爸这儿来\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.80,1:15:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哦我的天\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.84,1:15:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,来...\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.64,1:15:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸这儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.44,1:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-啊！- 弗兰克！\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Ah! -Frank!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.61,1:15:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnarial\fs12}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.64,1:16:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,猫和老鼠的游戏 到此为止了\N{\fnarial\fs12}so much for the cat-and-mouse shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.80,1:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fnarial\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.08,1:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别杀我！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Not me!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.04,1:16:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,无关个人感情 宝贝\N{\fnarial\fs12}It's nothing personal, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.20,1:16:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿 美人儿？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Where are you, beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.20,1:17:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,出来 出来 不论你在哪儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}Come out, come out, wherever you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.20,1:20:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦我的老天\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.06,1:20:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fnarial\fs12}Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.04,1:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别为他悲伤了\N{\fnarial\fs12}No, don't mourn him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.96,1:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们碰他前 他就已经死了\N{\fnarial\fs12}He was dead long before we ever touched him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.96,1:20:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 混蛋！ - 安静点儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}-Bastard! -Hush now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.37,1:20:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fnarial\fs12}Everything's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.48,1:20:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克在这儿\N{\fnarial\fs12}Frank's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.64,1:20:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.62,1:20:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你亲爱的弗兰克叔叔\N{\fnarial\fs12}Your dear old Uncle Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.00,1:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.31,1:21:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克\N{\fnarial\fs12}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.06,1:21:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fnarial\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.56,1:21:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须听你亲口陈述\N{\fnarial\fs12}We had to hear it from your own lips.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.88,1:21:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,此非为你所观瞻\N{\fnarial\fs12}This isn't for your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.02,1:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我下套\N{\fnarial\fs12}You set me up,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.76,1:21:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,婊子！\N{\fnarial\fs12}bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.20,1:22:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝哭泣\N{\fnarial\fs12}Jesus wept
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.60,1:23:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会如此仓促地离开我们吧？\N{\fnarial\fs12}Not leaving us so soon, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.96,1:23:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有无数奇观等待你领略\N{\fnarial\fs12}We have such sights to show you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.48,1:24:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 糟糕\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.58,1:24:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不！请勿如此！ - 下地狱吧！\N{\fnarial\fs12}-No! Don't do that! -Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.33,1:24:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Kirsty!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.48,1:24:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Kirsty!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.32,1:25:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnarial\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.37,1:25:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂夫\N{\fnarial\fs12}Steve.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.00,1:25:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不!\N{\fnarial\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.48,1:25:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 糟糕！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.67,1:25:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 克里斯蒂 谢天谢地 你没事\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, Kirsty! Thank God you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.36,1:25:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快离开这个鬼地方！马上！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Let's get the hell out of here! Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.48,1:25:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.21,1:25:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天啊 不\N{\fnarial\fs12}Oh, God. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.31,1:26:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快开门！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Open!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.76,1:26:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂夫！不要！\N{\fnarial\fs12}Steve! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.12,1:30:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,您看中什么 先生？\N{\fnarial\fs12}What's your pleasure, sir?

